subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Annika Sorenstam won the season-opening SBS Open in Kahuku, Hawaii, for her 70th L.P.G.A. Tour title and her first since September 2006. She birdied two of the last three holes for a three-under 69 and a two-stroke victory.
